Package org.encryptor4j.test

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AliceBobNetworkTest
    Unit test that performs a key agreement with a server over a TCP socket and sends a file to the server encrypted using the agreed shared secret.
    KeyAgreementTest
    Unit test that tests key agreement algorithms such as Diffie-Hellman and Elliptic Curve Diffie-Hellman.
    MaxAllowedKeyLengthTest
    Tests whether the Java Cryptography Extension (JCE) unlimited strength jurisdiction policy files have been installed.
    MessageTest
    Unit test that tests message encryption using the Encryptor class.
    StreamTest
    Unit test that tests AES streaming encryption with the Encryptor class.
    UtilTest
